Licenses for Sharing Software Code Non-Commercially
TDG-Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike
This license lets other researchers modify your source code and share it with other researchers provided they credit you for the original software and license under these same terms. Recommended for maximum freedom of other academic and non-commercial researchers.
